@*
    _Navigation.cshtml — navbar placeholder
    ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
    The static site ships an EMPTY <header id="navbar"> and lets
    navbar-component.js build the full pill navbar (logo, links, theme toggle,
    language switch, contact CTA, command-palette trigger, hamburger + mobile
    panel) via innerHTML. We keep that faithful client-injected approach so the
    ported navbar.js active-pill / scroll logic finds the elements it expects
    (migration: nav targets come from window.__navConfig.routes in _Layout).
*@
<header class="navbar" id="navbar"></header>
